{"tid":974414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圖劫女子格鬥手　男賊反被毆至面目全非","createTime":"2019-01-09T00:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:37.000Z","uid":53379,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"216c28b6c0f0e6c7392c852ddb58f8035fcd1921","tid":974414,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">圖劫女子格鬥手　男賊反被毆至面目全非</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190108/s00006/c0d4c79c9e31fc524608ea32fb1e8feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190108%2Fs00006%2Fc0d4c79c9e31fc524608ea32fb1e8feb.jpg&h=5db53bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190108/s00006/c0da2913a9c6e9bc5cc1a5d960fe4302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190108%2Fs00006%2Fc0da2913a9c6e9bc5cc1a5d960fe4302.jpg&h=009bfe24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3之2 - 維安娜(左)及賊人(右)(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n笨賊遇上武林高手，電視劇的情節，日前在巴西上演。一名女子終極綜合格鬥（UFC）好手，上周六遇上賊人襲擊，圖搶去她身上的手提電話，結果賊人反被打至臉容扭曲，引起格鬥界熱議。<br />\n<br />\n巴西女子綜合格鬥好手維安娜（Polyana Viana），上周六在里約熱內盧遇上可疑男子，後者上前扮作查問時間，然後自稱帶有武器，要求維安娜交出手提電話。維安娜此時處變不驚，當對方伸手作狀拿出手槍之際，施展兩拳及踢腿，並以頸鎖將賊人制服地上，然後對他說：「現在我們等警察來。」<br />\n<br />\nUFC主席Dana White事後上載圖片，展示賊人被打至臉容腫脹。26歲的維安娜在去年2月首戰UFC擂台，至今錄得10勝2負，對上一仗在去年8月UFC 227賽事即使落敗，但這次面對賊人依然游刃有餘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20190108/s00006/1546940568644/%E3%80%90%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E5%A5%87%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E5%9C%96%E5%8A%AB%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E6%89%8B-%E7%94%B7%E8%B3%8A%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86%E8%87%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%AE%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190108%2Fs00006%2F1546940568644%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%258A%25AB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%2589%258B-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B3%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2586%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%259E&d=Q7xW9EaYSPylzTvpwZPTJf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b9e276f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190108%2Fs00006%2F1546940568644%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%258A%25AB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%2589%258B-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B3%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2586%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%259E&h=ade6d318\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20190108/s00006/1546940568644/%E3%80%90%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E5%A5%87%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E5%9C%96%E5%8A%AB%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E6%89%8B-%E7%94%B7%E8%B3%8A%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86%E8%87%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%AE%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%9E</a>"},{"pid":"5659d0096e4b9a31975681dd6655ad93f3786ae2","tid":974414,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa28559295a6a00a2f0a4fe979df1f3f04a5a613","tid":974414,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d56f0adcc99b4be945bf5bfb94813608bc987f0","tid":974414,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"江湖上最惡毒既面目全非腳"},{"pid":"79230a2f273d9563a08118ccd56f3e02e5b5fc7d","tid":974414,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"如果佢識少林功夫⋯⋯"}]}